<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
  <h3>Payment has been received for invoice '<%= @invoice.id %>'</h3>
  <p>
    Hi <b><%= @work_order.task_owner_name %></b>
  </p>
  <p>
    We wanted to let you know that we have received payment for<br>
    <a href="<%= notifications_url %>/#/work_orders/<%= @work_order._id %>"><%= @work_order.task_title %></a>
  </p>
  <p>
    At this stage, your work order has been completed. We hope that everything went smoothly and
    expect that <b><%= @work_order.bid_owner_name %></b> did a great job for you. Please visit the
    work order and provide a review for this task if you haven't already done so.
  </p>
  <p>
    When you're ready, hop back on <%= site_name %> and <a href="<%= notifications_url %>/#/tasks/create">Post your next Project</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    Your feedback is always welcome.
    <a href="mailto:<%= @feedback_mailto %>">Drop us a line</a> any time!
  </p>
  <p>
    Sincerely,
  </p>
  <p>
    <em><%= site_signature %></em>
  </p>
</body>
</html>
